    <title>Electronic Barrette Hub</title>
    <updated>2018-08-04T00:00:00+02:00</updated>
    <content type="html">&lt;section id="electronic-barrette-hub"&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A base station of all your blinking lights&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="project-thumb"&gt;
&lt;a class="reference external image-reference" href="/_images/3523861540203435549.jpg"&gt;&lt;img alt="projects/project-160167/images/3523861540203435549.jpg" src="projects/project-160167/images/3523861540203435549.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
